    public interface Event4AsyncDelegate<T1,​T2,​T3,​T4>
extends Action4Async<T1,​T2,​T3,​T4>, Event4Delegate<T1,​T2,​T3,​T4>
    An Event4AsyncDelegate implements Action4Async as well as Event4Delegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action4Async interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the Event4Delegate interface.
